# controls.air — Agent Interpretation Reference

rationale_notes:
  - "Hunt input changes movement regime, not steering source."
  - "Keyboard steering has priority over pointer steering until pointer movement reactivates pointer control."
  - "Movement keys support layout equivalents where possible, and simultaneous keys compose direction."
  - "Fixed camera is a deliberate scope boundary for the current stage."

input_bindings:
  hunt: [ "Space", "mouse-button-held", "touch-held" ]
